resolve_sha(repo, ref):
- If ref=='latest', get latest release tag
- If ref is vX.Y.Z and repo is codeql-action, rewrite to codeql-bundle-vX.Y.Z
- Try to resolve tag to SHA
- If not found, try branch
- If sub-action and not found, fallback to latest bundle SHA
- Return SHA
